courses.customDesc: One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A23, A3, B2, C1, C2, C4, D1, D2, D3, D5 and F. C4, D5 and F should be taken only after Junior standing is reached (90 units). NO ARCH COURSE FOR C4, except ARCH 326. Refer to online catalog for GE course selection and Graduation Writing Requirement (GWR). USCP requirement can be satisfied by some (but not all) courses within GE categories: C3, D1, D3, D4, D5 or F.
